description: ConceptDraw DIAGRAM is an amateur and professional diagramming application for Windows and macOS. The software can create simple and complex processes, such as building plans and employee onboarding steps.

You can enhance the content in diagrams, flowcharts, and other drawings by adding shapes, icons, and other objects. To create a CDL file to store the shapes and objects, select File → Library → Save As .
NOTE: ConceptDraw DIAGRAM was previously ConceptDraw PRO.
